### Bonding of interfaces


## Repositories
### Activate EPEL repo
  epel_release=$(curl -sL http://download.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/i386/ | grep epel-release | sed s/.*\"\>// | sed s/\<.*//)
  cd /tmp
  wget http://download.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/i386/${epel_release}
  sudo rpm -ivh ${epel_release}




